{"title": "CentOS 6 添加网易163源 - 数据分析 ", "index": "yum,python,centos,linux", "content": "参考网站 http://mirrors.163.com/.help/...\n1.首先备份CentOS-Base.repo，如果以前未添加过163源，此步可以省略\ncd /etc/yum.repos.d/\nmv CentOS-Base.repo CentOS-Base.repo.backup\n2.下载163源\nwget http://mirrors.163.com/.help/CentOS6-Base-163.repo\n3.把下载文件改成源文件\nmv CentOS6-Base-163.repo CentOS-Base.repo\n4.运行以下命令生成缓存\nyum clean all\nyum makecache\nyum makecache可能出现以下错误:\nLoaded plugins: refresh-packagekit, security\nhttp://mirrors.163.com/centos/6Server/os/x86_64/repodata/repomd.xml: [Errno 14] PYCURL\nERROR 22 -\"The requested URL returned error: 404 Not Found\"\nTrying other mirror.\nError: Cannot retrieve repository metadata (repomd.xml) for repository: base. Please\nverify its path and try again\n我们尝试进入http://mirrors.163.com/centos...发现仍然是：404 Not Found\n这时我们进入http://mirrors.163.com/centos/发现：目录下有6 6.0-6.8目录，并没有6Server目录。猜测$releasever被错误地编译为：6Server;正确情况下应为6.4。（我的为CentOs6.4）\n我们需要把CentOS-Base.repo中的$releasever全部修改为6.4:\nvi CentOS-Base.repo\n# 在末行模式下执行以下：\n：%s/$releasever/6.4        # Esc -> Shift+: 进入末行模式\n# 修改完保存退出：Esc -> Shift+: -> wq\n重新运行\nyum makecache\n哈哈，可能仍然出现与之前相似的错误，如下：\nLoaded plugins: refresh-packagekit, security\nhttp://mirrors.163.com/centos/6.4/os/x86_64/repodata/repomd.xml: [Errno 14] PYCURL\nERROR 22 -\"The requested URL returned error: 404 Not Found\"\nTrying other mirror.\nError: Cannot retrieve repository metadata (repomd.xml) for repository: base. Please\nverify its path and try again\n再次进入 http://mirrors.163.com/centos/发现：目录下有6.4下只有readme文件，而6目录下具有完整的文件。所以我们需要再次修改一下：把6.4全部修改为6（如果怕一个个修改麻烦，可以重新下载源文件）如下：\nrm -rf CentOS-Base.repo         # 先删除6.4的源文件\nwget http://mirrors.163.com/.help/CentOS6-Base-163.repo    # 把下载文件改成源文件\nmv CentOS6-Base-163.repo CentOS-Base.repo\nyum clean all\nyum makecache\nDone！！！！！\n\n                ", "mainLikeNum": ["0 "], "mainBookmarkNum": "2"}